  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your<strong> pork loin steaks</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let them adjust to room temperature</p><p>Cut your<strong> potatoes </strong>(skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
