    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and cook for 8-10 min or until caramelised</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>caramelised onions</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
