      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the fat from the<strong> pork loin steaks</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> pork loin steaks</strong> finely</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced pork</strong> to the<strong> spicy marinade</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p>",
