    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are almost cooked, add your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until they're hot and crusty</p><p>Once done, carefully cut them in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
