    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated pork </strong>and any <strong>remaining marinade </strong>from the bowl<strong> </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until fragrant and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and cook for 30 secs further, stirring until the pork is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>Portuguese-style spicy pork</strong></p>",
