        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread the <strong>sweet mustard mayo</strong> over the<strong> warmed ciabattas </strong>and top with the <strong>Portuguese-style spicy pork </strong>and <strong>caramelised onions </strong>- this is your <strong>Portuguese-style spicy pork bifana sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> chips</strong> and<strong> salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: Don't forget to remove the bay leaf[ves]!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
